Ctrl-Tab
=========

About
=====

Use Ctrl-Tab by  is a plugin for Geany that provides a dialog for rapid switching to last used documents or tool windows.


Usage
=====

After having enabled the plugin inside Geany through Geany's plugin manager,
you'll need to setup a keybinding for triggering Ctrl-Tab. Go to
the preferences, and under the Keybindings tab set the *Commander -> Show Panel*
keybinding


